      "created_at": "2024-03-04T08:25:30.107Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I get this on my Tacx Neo (the old version) if I need to stop for the loo.  What I have found works for me is, as I start to ride again, I switch to slope mode for a few seconds and allow it to catch the watts and then switch back to ERG.  Not sure how and why it would make a difference and it could be coincidence but I tend to get the issue if I don\u2019t do that and don\u2019t have the problem if I do, so worth a try.</p>",
